snippet.title: Harvest Havoc Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Harvest Havoc now available to purchase on steam.

store.steampowered.com/app/2525490/Harvest_Havoc/

Gather your friends and get ready for a chaotic multiplayer PVP in a world of farming-themed extravaganza. With up to 6 players, compete against each other to become the ultimate farmer-warrior. Sow seeds, harvest bountiful crops, and peddle your produce for victory.
